<i>A group of elite mercenaries willing 
to take any job for the right price.</i>

348
00:22:59.020 --> 00:23:04.260
<i>Stanegger, the leader of Purple 
Meteor Storm, hides a secret.</i>

349
00:23:04.580 --> 00:23:08.730
<i>The fact that he has 
a loving wife and daughter.</i>

350
00:23:08.730 --> 00:23:13.940
<i>The enemy organization can 
never learn of their existence.</i>

351
00:23:13.700 --> 00:23:15.200
He must protect
his wife and daughter

352
00:23:15.490 --> 00:23:21.490
<i>Why did Stanegger, the infamous 
lone warrior, get married?</i>

353
00:23:21.770 --> 00:23:25.160
<i>Why does he continue to fight 
for Purple Meteor Storm?</i>

354
00:23:25.700 --> 00:23:30.860
<i>Is it weakness to have 
a family? To know of love?</i>

355
00:23:32.010 --> 00:23:33.510
What does it truly mean to be strong...?

356
00:23:32.790 --> 00:23:37.770
<i>Witness the gripping twists 
and turns that will leave you breathless!</i>

